# Vue Testing

> Extends [typescript/testing.md](../typescript/testing.md) and [common/testing.md](../common/testing.md).

## Stack

- **Vitest** + **@vue/test-utils** (preferred for Vite projects)
- Mount with `global.plugins` for Pinia and Router stubs

## Component tests

- Test behavior and emitted events, not implementation details
- Use `data-testid` or roles for queries; avoid brittle CSS selectors
- Stub child components when testing parent orchestration

## Composable tests

- Test composables with `withSetup` helper or mount dummy component
- Mock `fetch` / API layer, not internal refs

## E2E

- Critical flows: login, main CRUD path, payment if applicable
- Delegate full E2E to `@e2e-runner` when scope is cross-page

## Coverage

- Target 80% over time; prioritize stores, composables, and form validation
